<br>
The guardian sent her sword quickly across the thigh of the man to her left, spinning then the sword finding a home in the other's ribcage.  Picking her booted foot out of the thick muck of mud, she slammed it against his chest.  Pulling out her sword as he fell to the ground.  <br>
<br>
The first began to charge her, but it only led to her sword finding a home in his heart.  Marpe still had no expression as she ripped her sword out of the second man.<br>
<br>
Now free to do as she was asked, Marpe ran to Hippolyte side.  Standing opposite of Elektra, Marpe could see that the Queen was weak.  &quot;Hippolyte, come.  Let's get you to a horse.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Platinum Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 912<br> <font color=#993300>(5/1/03 1:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=204>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Attack Begins</span><hr size=1> Hippolyte walked out beside Elektra and smiled when she was greeted by Alysia.  She would have saluted, had the pain in her side not been so strong.  &quot;Good to see you, Alysia.&quot;  Then seeing the northern queen take off, Hippolyte looked thru the rain at her fighting athelfi.<br>
